'''里辛學校'''是英國傳統[[私立|私立]]學校，提供日校和寄宿，共有約300名學生，大部分是國際生，目的是確保校園提供多元文化環境，讓學生之間互相激發<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ohpama.com/53807/overseas/%E3%80%90samuel%E3%80%91%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E7%A5%9E%E5%A5%87%E5%9B%9B%E6%A0%A1%EF%BC%8Dcardiff-sixth-form-college-ruthin-school/ |title=英國神奇四校－Cardiff Sixth Form College & Ruthin School |access-date=2019-11-08 |archive-date=2020-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200130154035/http://www.ohpama.com/53807/overseas/%E3%80%90samuel%E3%80%91%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E7%A5%9E%E5%A5%87%E5%9B%9B%E6%A0%A1%EF%BC%8Dcardiff-sixth-form-college-ruthin-school/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該校位於北[[威爾士|威爾士]][[登比郡|登比郡]][[里辛|里辛]]的郊區。創立於1284年，自1990年起成男女同校。

==教育==
在學校網頁上，校長貝爾菲爾德先生說：「我們學校在『獨立學校』督察報告呈現非常良好的結果，並不僅是在學術成果上的評價最為正面，學生的積極態度也值得一提。」 <ref> [http://www.ruthinschool.co.uk/about/the_principals_message.php www.ruthinschool website; accessed 18/06/2014] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140624054251/http://ruthinschool.co.uk/about/the_principals_message.php |date=2014-06-24 }} </ref>

多年來，該校學生都持續在A Level獲得極佳成績，2015年的A Level成績，72.25%的學生達到的成績分別為A*或A。這學校在Best Schools 的男女同校寄宿學校排行表中排第4名<ref>[http://www.best-schools.co.uk/uk-school-league-tables/co-educational-boarding-schools/] {{Wayback|url=http://www.best-schools.co.uk/uk-school-league-tables/co-educational-boarding-schools/ |date=20170422130148 }};Best Schools website; accessed 28/12/2015</ref>，和在英國每日電訊報的全國獨立學校排行表中排第34名<ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/leaguetables/11816732/A-level-results-2015-Independent-schools-results-table.html] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/leaguetables/11816732/A-level-results-2015-Independent-schools-results-table.html |date=20191227093912 }}; The Telegraph website; accessed 28/12/2015</ref>

在2019年的A Level成績，82%的學生達到的成績分別為A*或A。這學校在英國每日電訊報的獨立學校排行表中排第7名<ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/leaguetables/10262340/A-level-results-2013-Independent-schools-results-table.html] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/leaguetables/10262340/A-level-results-2013-Independent-schools-results-table.html |date=20210427201018 }}; The Telegraph website; accessed 18/06/2014</ref>，和在Best Schools 的男女同校寄宿學校排行表中排第13名。<ref>[http://www.best-schools.co.uk/uk-school-league-tables/co-educational-boarding-schools/] {{Wayback|url=http://www.best-schools.co.uk/uk-school-league-tables/co-educational-boarding-schools/ |date=20170422130148 }};Best Schools website; accessed 18/06/2014</ref>

根據2014年的[[Estyn|Estyn]]檢驗報告，十四至十六歳學生的英語和數學水平是遠高於威爾士的平均水平，今年十一年級的學生達到2級門檻的百分比也高於威爾士的平均水平。預科(A-Level)學生的成績平均遠高於威爾士3級的門檻。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.estyn.gov.uk/english/provider/6636027/ |title=Estyn Inspection Report; accessed 18/06/2014 |access-date=2014-06-18 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714165104/http://www.estyn.gov.uk/english/provider/6636027/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

